tivated with a strong sense of ownership.<br /> </li></ul><p><strong>Preferred Skills</strong></p><ul><li>Experience with SQL and relational databases. </li><li>Exposure to test automation frameworks. </li><li>Experience supporting production systems and end users.</li><li>Experience working in global or enterprise environments.</li></ul>",
